Every Kalmykia resident is a debtor .
Residents of the republic increasingly visit the official website of the Federal Service of the Russian judicial officers for the Republic of Kazakhstan.
According to the specialists of the department of organizational and control work, informatization and ensuring information security of the republican department, over 140 thousand visits to the site itself were registered in the past eight months, more than 42 thousand - to the section "Data Bank of executive proceedings", 661 payment receipts for payment of debts were downloaded.
According to the Chairman of the Public Council under the Federal Social Service of Russia in the Republic of Kazakhstan, Valery Bogdanov, almost every resident of the region has debts for utility payments, fines of the traffic police, bank loans, and no one is insured against unforeseen situations.
But debtors can expect negative consequences, such as a travel ban.
That is why the Federal Service for the Protection of the Family in Russia recommends that all those who plan to travel abroad should check with the bailiffs' department at the place of residence or on the website www.r08fssprus.ru for information on the existence of unpaid debts and repay them.
The service has created the "Data Bank of Executive Proceedings" for the convenience of citizens.
This special electronic application is available not only on the regional websites of the Federal Service for the Protection of the Public Interest of Russia, but also on social networks and mobile communication devices such as iPads, iPhones and smartphones.
The data bank contains information about the enforcement proceedings initiated by the Kalmyk Prosecutor's Office against all debtors, - explains the assistant of the head of the Federal Criminal Police Service of Russia in the Republic of Kazakhstan, Delgir Bodgaeva.
"If there is a debt, the system displays information about the number and date of initiation of enforcement proceedings; the name of the authority that issued the execution sheet or other act; its number, amount and type of debt; the address of the judicial officers' department; the surname of the court officer-executor; contact telephone.
Information on the execution procedure can also be obtained on the portal of state services at the address: http://epgu.gosuslugi.ru"
