First of all, the loss of sovereignty.
It is obvious that there are countries that would not want Macedonia to remain one of the sovereign countries in the Balkans".
Fey Dülgeri, Euronews: "The former Yugoslav Republic of Macedonia is facing the biggest challenge in its history.
